<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3609.6.1>
    bibo:endPage "567" ;
    bibo:issue "6" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "521" ;
    bibo:volume "3609" ;
    dc:creator "Anderson, Owen F." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "A review of New Zealand and southeast Australian echinothuriinids (Echinodermata: Echinothuriidae) with descriptions of seven new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219313>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219314>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219315>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219317>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219318> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219313>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Araeosoma bidentatum sp. nov., holotype, NIWA 23720 (131 mm TD). Left, aboral view; right, oral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219313/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219314>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Araeosoma bidentatum sp. nov., holotype, NIWA 23720. Details of coronal plates. Top, aboral; bottom, oral; left, ambulacra; right, interambulacra." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219314/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219315>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Primary spine sections (left, oral; right, aboral). A, Araeosoma migratum (NIWA 45089); B, A. bakeri (NIWA 6564); C, Hapalosoma amynina (NIWA 6621); D, A. tertii (NIWA 29453); E, A. alternatum (NIWA 53579); F, A. anatirostrum (NIWA 29442); G, A. thetidis (NIWA 29419); H, A. bidentatum (NIWA 23720); I, A. leppienae (NIWA 23724)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219317>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Araeosoma bidentatum sp. nov., holotype, NIWA 23720. SEM images of appendages. A & B, valves of triphyllous pedicellariae; C & D, distal valve tips of dactylous pedicellariae; E, a sphaeridium; F & G, valves of bidentate pedicellariae; H & I, valves of large involute tridentate pedicellariae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219317/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219318>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Araeosoma bidentatum sp. nov. Distribution of confirmed records within the New Zealand region, from material examined. Number of records = 13. The dashed line is the 1000 m depth contour." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

